{"tid":728759,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"小米計劃明年進軍美國手機市場  高級副總裁：正開發定制機型","createTime":"2018-07-04T03:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T04:23:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4d97c2dc88e1502cd642e508f1abc50d1596e2","tid":728759,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"新浪科技訊北京時間7月4日早間消息，小米正計劃於明年進入美國市場，這家智能手機製造商表示，美國的合作夥伴可以幫助他們繞開一些本國競爭對手所遇到的阻力。<br />\n<br />\n小米集團高級副總裁王翔本週二對路透社表示，美國市場&ldquo;非常有吸引力&rdquo;，該公司正在增加工程資源，開發與美國網絡兼容的機型。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;明年我們希望能在那裡有所作為，&rdquo;王翔說。 他還補充，與美國運營商的談判尚未達成具體協議。<br />\n<br />\n王翔表示，中美貿易的緊張局勢引發了&ldquo;不確定性&rdquo;，但他淡化了當前局勢對該公司美國擴張計劃的影響，突出強調該公司與美國芯片製造商高通和谷歌母公司Alphabet等供應商的關係。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們沒有任何理由介入政治問題，&rdquo;王翔說，他在2015年加入小米之前，負責運營高通在中國的業務。<br />\n<br />\n他說，小米公司密切關註消費市場，許多工程師和投資者都來自美國。<br />\n<br />\n下週一，小米股票將在港股上市，此前該公司的IPO發行價格處其標價區間的底部，但這家成立8年的創業公司仍被看好，目前其資產估值約為540億美元。<br />\n<br />\n小米集團現在是印度最大的智能手機供應商，並且向包括西班牙和俄羅斯在內的歐洲市場進軍。 不過，最近該公司面臨低成本競爭對手的多重夾擊，在中國的市場份額有所下降。 （斯眉）<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：張玉潔SF107<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fworld%2Fgjcj%2F2018-07-04%2Fdoc-ihevauxk0895812.shtml&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com.hk%2Ftranslate%3Fsl%3Dzh-CN%26tl%3Dzh-TW%26js%3Dy%26prev%3D_t%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26ie%3DUTF-8%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Ffinance.sina.com.cn%252Fworld%252Fgjcj%252F2018-07-04%252Fdoc-ihevauxk0895812.shtml%26edit-text%3D%26act%3Durl&d=Eb0W3O0KtXZ08nsU8PCOajACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=7787e456\" target=\"_blank\">https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=zh-CN&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fworld%2Fgjcj%2F2018-07-04%2Fdoc-ihevauxk0895812.shtml&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330b83e936bd93da66e70de62c179ca029477bb4","tid":728759,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國fatfat"},{"pid":"6d3d6cb46af0b35d3d4e60e6440132523b243b74","tid":728759,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"330b83e936bd93da66e70de62c179ca029477bb4","tid":728759,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國fatfat"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"唔多信會俾佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabdd859d24d4e5eb59adafdacaf60740c62ea26","tid":728759,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"而家仲咁容易入美國市場"},{"pid":"8f8b9835deff2b6897f1a63a277f8bcc87eb0707","tid":728759,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"走去重注買佢股票都戇撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e7de344d2e1810b7c4d26557fb6cd6633cf1cf","tid":728759,"uid":34641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"鬼會俾你入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a5678ebf6316fd0bafeee28dc48328919b803b","tid":728759,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"一陣侵侵講句唔比你入來玩就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663b156cc4076aed9371914d084893debfd196f4","tid":728759,"uid":158613,"like"